user_query: show me the total amount by account type
raw_agent_output:
To get the total amount by account type, the SQL query is:

SELECT account_type, SUM(Amount) AS total_amount  
FROM consumption
GROUP BY account_type;

This will return the account type and the sum of the Amount column grouped by the account_type column.
